Roshni Joshi of Google's Chicago office will speak to you about her career and experience at Google, and what she loves about working in Chicago.  Led by ChicagoNEXT of World Business Chicago and the University of Illinois System, ThinkChicago connects top-tier university talent with local innovative companies. Especially during COVID-19, ThinkChicago is committed to support university students to explore career-building opportunities and engage with Chicago technology companies who are hiring during these challenging times. ThinkChicago’s TechTalk with UIC’s College of Engineering is an informative event exclusive for UIC students to hear directly from a Chicago tech leader, learn more about the city’s dynamic tech ecosystem, and get the latest updates from ThinkChicago upcoming programs.
